全好似轉左第二個民族咁話香港人中國一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而香港又話返人繁體支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"當你過去台仔地方覺得人地睇唔起港仔既時候, 台仔過黎連登一樣日日見到港仔笑鳩佢地D女全部係雞, 繁體大陸咁. 台灣人好定香港人好, 當心智真係成長左既時候就會對呢D 撩交嘈既網友既 COMMENTS 一笑置之."},{"pid":"d41a16f30038b93d960467b9835237fce8c14077","tid":775322,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e311c6d0c104856f0a5a67ea8d5e78eb1f636700","tid":775322,"uid":133206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"327fcb334ef010e05618a629f68c84eaf6f86d4f","tid":775322,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58b774bd83a2273ce39c55ed62a997e9f4619c16","tid":775322,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"台灣個D已經唔係小學雞咁簡單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"Fb d group成日見地佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"你見唔到香港嗰啲因為佢地玩緊抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個地方啲小學雞都咁on9架啦 定你覺得香港嘅都好正常無問題?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"我無講過香港好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你講到我唔知香港D中小學生點做咩啫 你又知我無見過 定係你唔知台灣個D點劣呀"},{"pid":"62ad89ebf1eb912638d0f34392cf8f42b819c3ea","tid":775322,"uid":133206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d41a16f30038b93d960467b9835237fce8c14077","tid":775322,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e311c6d0c104856f0a5a67ea8d5e78eb1f636700","tid":775322,"uid":133206,"like":0,"dislike":0